{"word":"ἐξαιρέω","slug":"ἐξαιρέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἐξαιρέω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐξ\">ἐξ</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:αἱρέω\">αἱρέω</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘remove from a place’, a bodily organ, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ act.\">act.</a> <b>take out, extract <a href='B:470 5:29'>Mt 5:29</a>; <a href='B:470 18:9'>18:9</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> in extended sense of removing from peril, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ mid.\">mid.</a> <b>deliver, rescue <a href='B:510 7:10'>Ac 7:10</a>, <a href='B:510 7:34'>34</a>; <a href='B:510 12:11'>12:11</a>; <a href='B:510 23:27'>23:27</a>; <a href='B:510 26:17'>26:17</a></b> (<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> vv. 21f on specific perils); <b><a href='B:550 1:4'>Gal 1:4</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐξάγω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐξαίρω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}